org.wikidata.wdtk.datamodel.interfaces

Interface TermedDocument

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EntityDocument
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ItemDocument, PropertyDocument
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ItemDocumentImpl, PropertyDocumentImpl, TermedDocumentImpl

    public interface TermedDocument
extends EntityDocument
    Interface for EntityDocuments that can be described by terms in several languages. These terms consist labels, descriptions, and aliases.
    Author:
    Markus Kroetzsch
